ringer - om polarhelter - og mye annet - allerede i f\u00f8r sommerferien, og mer kommer til h\u00f8sten."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "nyheter|trondheim|byenvarres"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c4e5c15342366cfef8116ce55e17bd65dbe5781279af065f7c648a470d56cbaa"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-03T12:36:59.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Den ene bor i Sverdrups vei, den andre i Hjalmar Johansens. N\u00e5 vil de vite mer om livet til de gamle norske polarheltene."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1203985.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/polhoegda1"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/226c65ad70ce51df269a403b4e26509734947853.jpg?598b1c27"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "By\u00e5singer lever blant polfarere -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "226c65ad70ce51df269a403b4e26509734947853"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "byenvarres"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "hobbies-and-interests"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["velforening", "levd", "polarhelter", "navn", "norske polarheltene", "norsk", "konge"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["polh\u00f8gda", "stina njaastad", "sverreslia", "sverdrups"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["marienberg", "oslo", "svalbard", "ila"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["oscar wisting", "hjalmar riiser-larsen", "fridtjof nansens", "maria reitan", "sigrid undset", "kristin lavr